' Notes
note right of AI
  Google Gemini AI
  - Natural Language Processing
  - Case Analysis
  - Evidence Evaluation
  - Legal Recommendations
end note

note right of UC18
  AI Analysis includes:
  - Summary generation
  - Confidence scoring
  - Category classification
  - Evidence priority
  - Recommended actions
end note

note bottom of UC6
  Case creation captures:
  - Title & Description
  - Priority & Category
  - Location & Date
  - Parties Involved
  - Initial Evidence
end note

note left of UC32
  Admin privileges:
  - User management
  - System-wide access
  - Report generation
  - Configuration control
end note

@enduml
